trend_summary: From earliest to latest imagery, tree-dominated suburbs persist while incremental infill thickens housing grids. The eastern industrial/commercial zone expands with new white-roof warehouses and larger parking lots. A central arterial corridor is widened and commercial frontage intensifies. Reservoir water levels fluctuate but shoreline stabilisation appears after mid-period. Overall change is gradual suburban consolidation rather than wholesale urbanisation.
